info.abstract: The User Session Map allows the import of a mapping file for users and sessions. The only acceptable column headers for user session map are in the following order: user_sess, user_id.
info.description: This component allows import a mapping file for users and sessions map.

outputs.b: A tab delimited file containing mappings for users and sessions
